198.init_model_answer: Yes, the logic is sound. If a subset of office supplies (which includes paper clips) are made of metal, it follows that a subset of paper clips are also made of metal.

199.question:
Is this logically sound?
Outlets are electrical fittings.
a subset of electrical fittings are surge-protected.
therefore, a subset of outlets are surge-protected.
199.init_model_answer: Yes, the logic is sound. If some electrical fittings (a category that includes outlets) are surge-protected, it follows that some outlets could also be surge-protected.
